name: Force of Nature
additional_notices:
The following token has a variable tax function on the smart contract to change tax rates post deployment.
Do your own research and be careful if you are trading this token.

description.en:
The game is a P2E and multiplayer and will also let you play vs. AI to sharpen your skills before your friends see you on the PvP-battlefield. FON will be bringing forth a P2E Game, Staking Platform and Suite of NFTs.

Alongside Mr Bapple — the boxing apple, you’ll be able to play with and against many other characters.

Hand-DrawnCharacters Each and every character, or Fruitarrior and Vegelante has been hand-drawn on a piece of paper, later made into digital 2D art and then 3D for the game.
